<h1>Real Estate Regulatory Authority and Appellate Tribunal</h1>
<div class="drop_shadow_sm"></div>

<p>Government of Bihar is the appropriate Government under the Act for the State of Bihar in terms of clause (g) of Section 2 of this Act. Exercising the power conferred by the third proviso to sub-section (1) of section 20 and first proviso to sub section (4) of section 43 of the Act, The Government of Bihar has designated The Principal Secretary, Urban development and Housing Department, Government of Bihar as the Regulatory Authority and The Bihar Land Tribunal, as the Appellate Tribunal respectively vide Notification nos. 348 & 349 and 346 & 347 dated 28th April 2017.</p>



  
